General.Name: BBI Bürgerliches Brauhaus Immobilien AG
General.Description: BBI Bürgerliches Brauhaus Immobilien AG operates as a real estate company in Germany. The company engages in the acquisition, rental, and management of retail properties. Its portfolio includes shopping centers and retail parks. The company is headquartered in Ingolstadt, Germany. BBI Bürgerliches Brauhaus Immobilien AG is a subsidiary of VIB Vermögen AG.
